OL,3,CFormer Ulster Unionist leader Steve
OL,4,CAiken suspended from Assembly for two
OL,5,Cdays
OL,7,FFormer Ulster Unionist leader Steve
OL,8,FAiken has been suspended from the
OL,9,FNorthern Ireland Assembly for two days.
OL,11,FThe sanction comes after a complaint
OL,12,Fthat he had breached the Assembly
OL,13,FMembers' Code of Conduct by disclosing
OL,14,Fconfidential information in 2021.
OL,16,FThe complaint was investigated by the
OL,17,Findependent Assembly Commissioner for
OL,18,FStandards Dr Melissa McCullough.
