OL,4,CAiken suspended from Assembly for two
OL,5,Cdays
OL,7,FFollowing her investigation report in
OL,8,FMarch 2022, the Committee on Standards
OL,9,Fand Privileges concluded that Mr Aiken
OL,10,Fhad breached the code through the
OL,11,Funauthorised disclosure of
OL,12,Fconfidential information relating to a
OL,13,Flive complaint and by failing to co-
OL,14,Foperate at all times with the
OL,15,Fcommissioner's investigation.
OL,17,FThe committee recommended that Mr
OL,18,FAiken be excluded from Assembly
OL,19,Fproceedings for a period of two
OL,20,Fsitting days.
