OL,7,FDuring its plenary sitting on Tuesday,
OL,8,Fthe Assembly backed the recommendation.
OL,10,FThe suspension will apply on May 13-14
OL,11,Fand will include Assembly committee
OL,12,Fmeetings.
OL,14,FMr Aiken responded in the Assembly
OL,15,Fsaying he respected the committee's
OL,16,Fjudgment and accepted the outcome of
OL,17,Fits deliberations.
