OL,7,FIn a statement, chairwoman of the
OL,8,FCommittee on Standards and Privileges
OL,9,FCaral Ni Chuilin said while the
OL,10,Fcommittee takes all breaches of the
OL,11,Fcode very seriously, "it noted the
OL,12,Fconclusion of the last committee that
OL,13,Fthis was an egregious breach", in
OL,14,Freference to Mr Aiken being a member
OL,15,Fof the committee.
